   end
end

function make_concat(list)
  return function (arg)
           local sep = (arg and arg[1]) or ", "
           local size = #list
           for i, e in ipairs(list) do
             if type(e) == "table" then
               if i ~= size then
                 yield(e)
                 yield(sep, true)
               else
                 yield(e)
               end
             else
               if i ~= size then
                 yield{ it = e }
                 yield(sep, true)
               else
                 yield{ it = e }
               end
             end
           end
         end
end
